Wiki / notebook for each project in [CLAUDE.md](../CLAUDE.md). Tasks live in [TASKS.md](../TASKS.md); use this for context, decisions, open questions, and longer-form thinking.

## How this works
- One folder per project, keyed to the codename in CLAUDE.md.
- Each folder has an `index.md` (the project's main wiki page). Add sub-files (`meetings.md`, `decisions.md`, `<event>-2026.md`, etc.) inside when a project grows.
- Cross-link other notes with `[[folder-name]]` (e.g. `[[example-project]]`). Linking to a not-yet-created note is fine — it just marks something worth writing later.
- New project? Copy `_template/index.md` into `notes/<codename-kebab>/index.md` and add a row below.

